  "body": "### What is wrong?\r\n\r\nCurrent logging output while fast syncing is:\r\n\r\n```\r\n    INFO  10-22 15:24:36       FastChainSyncer  Advanced by 26 blocks in 5.0 seconds, new head: #4924209\r\n    INFO  10-22 15:24:49       FastChainSyncer  Advanced by 36 blocks in 13.1 seconds, new head: #4924245\r\n    INFO  10-22 15:24:54       FastChainSyncer  Advanced by 89 blocks in 5.0 seconds, new head: #4924334\r\n    INFO  10-22 15:24:59       FastChainSyncer  Advanced by 66 blocks in 5.0 seconds, new head: #4924400\r\n    INFO  10-22 15:25:04       FastChainSyncer  Advanced by 8 blocks in 5.0 seconds, new head: #4924408\r\n    INFO  10-22 15:25:09       FastChainSyncer  Advanced by 51 blocks in 5.0 seconds, new head: #4924459\r\n    INFO  10-22 15:25:14       FastChainSyncer  Advanced by 58 blocks in 5.0 seconds, new head: #4924517\r\n    INFO  10-22 15:25:19       FastChainSyncer  Advanced by 51 blocks in 5.0 seconds, new head: #4924568\r\n    INFO  10-22 15:25:24       FastChainSyncer  Advanced by 36 blocks in 5.0 seconds, new head: #4924604\r\n    INFO  10-22 15:25:29       FastChainSyncer  Advanced by 67 blocks in 5.0 seconds, new head: #4924671\r\n```\r\n\r\nThis is nice, but it could be better.\r\n\r\n### How can it be fixed\r\n\r\nUpdate the logging output to contain the following.\r\n\r\n- number of blocks processed since last logging msg\r\n- total number of transactions in each block\r\n- EMA of blocks-per-second\r\n- amount of time elapsed since last logging msg\r\n- current head block number\r\n- current head block hash in format `\"<first-3-bytes-hex><unicode-elipsis><last-3-bytes-hex>\"`\r\n- age of the head block in format `1m2w9h`\r\n\r\n```\r\nblocks=<num-blocks>  txs=<num-txns>  bps=<blocks-per-second-ema>  elapsed=<time-since-last-msg>  num=<head-block-number>  hash=<head-block-hash> age=<head-block-age>\r\n```",
